snippet.title: Orompaquenga | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Orompaquega, a bizzare RPG with no class restriction where you play as a knight of the depths. Your goal is to defeat The Mass, a colossal floating ball of grease that will block the hole in the sky in no time, turning the World of the Depths to hell like in the old times.

Download the game at: https://isopodomancer.itch.io/orompaquenga

Follow me on twitter for more: https://twitter.com/isopodomancer
